@ApiGateway_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000
@Token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Gateway Info
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/
Accept: application/json

### Gateway Swagger UI
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/swagger

### Gateway Health Check
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###
### IDENTITY SERVICE
###

### Register User
POST {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/identity/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@evently.com",
  "password": "Test123!",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User"
}

### Login
POST {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/identity/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@evently.com",
  "password": "Test123!"
}

### Identity Service Health
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/identity/health
Accept: application/json

###
### EVENT SERVICE
###

### Get All Events
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/events
Accept: application/json

### Get Event by ID
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/events/1
Accept: application/json

### Create Event (Requires Auth)
POST {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

{
  "title": "Test Event",
  "description": "Test Description",
  "location": "Test Location",
  "startDate": "2025-12-01T19:00:00",
  "endDate": "2025-12-01T23:00:00",
  "capacity": 100,
  "price": 50.00
}

### Event Service Health
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/events/health
Accept: application/json

